{"tid":939542,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實人生根本係一層又一層嘅謊言","createTime":"2018-12-13T08:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T03:18:28.000Z","uid":206224,"like":3634,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":117,"replies":[{"pid":"a82d10d4882f42a3f49bda8e19bee117e1a396ff","tid":939542,"uid":206224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:21:25.000Z","msg":"由小學開始，老師就開始兇鳩你話記缺點會對未來有好大影響<br />\n讀緊中學果陣，師長話努力讀書考到入大學就可以日日玩<br />\n辛苦入到大學之後，讀書刷GPA之餘仲要搏命刷CV做實習，因為個個都話到時入到份高薪厚職就可以呼風喚雨<br />\n點知就算你畢業做到專業人士，你都只不過係一個要攬曬所有屎黎做嘅低層。你個老闆會同你講：拿，你日日爆肝OT係有回報嘅，捱兩三年之後升職，到時咩福利都有你嘆<br />\n勞勞役役三年後，你發覺老闆根本無諗過升你職，人工加得雞碎咁多之餘，其他福利反而cut q埋。好唔忿氣嘅你聽到同事話，阿Tom係間公司做5年之後成功跳槽入到去in-house，可以日日點鳩外面嘅人做野，幾撚爽皮<br />\n你憑住呢個信念捱到有5年經驗，如願以償跳槽入到去in-house。點知你發覺間公司一樣要OT到凌晨，人工升幅都係追唔到物價，因為香港老闆根本大部分都係刻薄吸血鬼黎。As long as你仲係香港呢個圈子到，你就永遠係要被壓逼果個。<br />\n<br />\n有晚，你如常OT到凌晨先返到屋企，沖完涼之後臨訓打開facebook望下<br />\n你見到中學果個成日比老師鬧死蠢，入唔到大學嘅Johnny仔post左張好靚嘅日本風景相。<br />\nJohnny仔中學畢業就去日本一間拉麵店做學徒，日日準時開工收工，個日本老闆都好均真地將一切所識用心教Johnny仔。幾年之後，Johnny仔跟師傅返去日本總店做野，靠工作簽證拎埋永住權。雖然人工唔高，但而家有一棟自己嘅獨立屋，兩架車，同老婆恩恩愛愛咁生活落去，weekend都可以揸車去趟road trip。<br />\n你不禁反問自己，明明你聽曬師長所講，付出比其他人更多嘅努力，拎住份叫做OK嘅人工。點解你嘅生活質素依然每況越下，甚至要比Johnny仔漸漸拋離？<br />\n呢一晚你突然領悟到，香港根本係個超巨型奴隸社會。上層嘅人呃鳩中層人，中層人再呃鳩下層人，誘導班奴隸繼續係香港賣命，為班上層嘅人做狗。<br />\n殺人放火金腰帶，修橋補路無屍骸。<br />\n係香港做野嘅人生，根本只係一層又一層嘅謊言。"},{"pid":"b7bbd1262a47a654b91c3e561fe53c0f664fa1a0","tid":939542,"uid":188387,"like":511,"dislike":4,"score":507,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:26:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f65f3bfbab6bcbf863f0f501ea2cf4cb48d038c","tid":939542,"uid":155197,"like":240,"dislike":27,"score":213,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:27:52.000Z","msg":"好心你勤力D,唔好咁懶啦"},{"pid":"ec4e058edf4b0ed09387a9ee85ca7867d501749c","tid":939542,"uid":20025,"like":44,"dislike":3,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:28:57.000Z","msg":"不要再說了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27dfd78d93b7d366d713e71640ef84031b4a14ed","tid":939542,"uid":140769,"like":3,"dislike":113,"score":-110,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:30:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5313e6387d20bfbad199389cab57a09ae0cf8e61","tid":939542,"uid":31275,"like":341,"dislike":3,"score":338,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:32:13.000Z","msg":"香港做野學歷只不過係入場劵,識人多,識玩手段先至有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 奈何我乜都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97267a24c6101d3fe7852fe12ef3d4712eb44f49","tid":939542,"uid":37133,"like":78,"dislike":3,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:32:58.000Z","msg":"屌好似講緊自己個人生咁<br />\n巴打又係legal?<br />\n<br />\n(廁所透氣中)"},{"pid":"ff1c948a523f9fe505cee3f3417bfa143c456166","tid":939542,"uid":214534,"like":270,"dislike":6,"score":264,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:32:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁係你出身窮撚階層<br />\n要捱得比人地其他人辛苦姐<br />\n大把人都係打份濕鳩工<br />\n但人地屋企一早諗住留層供斷既樓俾佢<br />\n輕輕鬆鬆冇壓力</span>"},{"pid":"c8ed48bada03579349c07c3334d169bc47aafd43","tid":939542,"uid":62337,"like":150,"dislike":19,"score":131,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:33:13.000Z","msg":"因為你無用腦獨立地思考同為自己打算 剩係識聽人點 <br />\n順便可以賴埋環境造成自己咁"},{"pid":"a70ebb273460e3a16e00605c26932417d08a519c","tid":939542,"uid":133528,"like":1,"dislike":53,"score":-52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:33:57.000Z","msg":"我沒有說謊 我何必說謊<br />\n妳知道的 我缺點之一就是很健忘<br />\n我哪有說謊<br />\n是很感謝今晚的相伴 但我竟然有些不習慣"},{"pid":"cf3d502d04e296c61c33d54ab78c2032b37d6c00","tid":939542,"uid":64743,"like":111,"dislike":1,"score":110,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:34:27.000Z","msg":"強者賦予你生存方式，價值觀<br />\n唔係佢點管你，使你？<br />\n個個都係發財扮立品<br />\n你幾時見過人日行一善行到發達<br />\n殺最多人就坐權力頂峰，你睇隻雜種"},{"pid":"f30d34e256a8fe136270b0003821e5d0fb2d4dc4","tid":939542,"uid":199639,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:35:52.000Z","msg":"諗咁多做咩啊<br />\n做嘢啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90108081fd3a33882ee19bb326a851d4a0286e25","tid":939542,"uid":64009,"like":13,"dislike":78,"score":-65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:36:30.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n屋企成日話細個唔讀書<br />\n大左做乞衣<br />\n結果會考得554444<br />\n迫住去外國讀書<br />\n讀完番來屋企比左層樓我<br />\n依家日日噤股票渡日<br />\n慘"},{"pid":"673dd5f6343a2ce40ea9e81bbd2a625ff3daad84","tid":939542,"uid":75692,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:38:44.000Z","msg":"但你諗深一層<br />\n你無讀書<br />\n將來都難出走香港"},{"pid":"b1e9781fc81b9f6f594d42be77d0c97cd7e04674","tid":939542,"uid":206224,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"quote":{"pid":"97267a24c6101d3fe7852fe12ef3d4712eb44f49","tid":939542,"uid":37133,"like":78,"dislike":3,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:32:58.000Z","msg":"屌好似講緊自己個人生咁<br />\n巴打又係legal?<br />\n<br />\n(廁所透氣中)"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:39:01.000Z","msg":"同路人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公司有個同事次次都忍尿忍到最後一刻先去廁所<br />\n每次都聽到佢d痾尿聲勁大力，我遲過佢入去痾，我痾完洗埋手走佢都未痾完，成日都覺得佢咁樣好慘"},{"pid":"b4541f52120fb1e1700f49cd41cdf71177cbd73c","tid":939542,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670b55f4b2f6e8828a0b9fee8317d68a4c9ee864","tid":939542,"uid":196625,"like":56,"dislike":2,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:43:29.000Z","msg":"你讀完書先明自己點解窮架嘛<br />\n<br />\n香港 係吹到好大個條友先會成功<br />\n真係落手做個個係做到仆街<br />\n<br />\n吹到好大個個唔洗負責?<br />\n要負責之前佢跳槽走撚左啦<br />\n所以馬時亨咪傻西囉<br />\n次次都係未爆鑊都唔願走"},{"pid":"5586bf1df106dc8b77a56ec2a31d7ecdd76c40eb","tid":939542,"uid":64743,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b1e9781fc81b9f6f594d42be77d0c97cd7e04674","tid":939542,"uid":206224,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"quote":{"pid":"97267a24c6101d3fe7852fe12ef3d4712eb44f49","tid":939542,"uid":37133,"like":78,"dislike":3,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:32:58.000Z","msg":"屌好似講緊自己個人生咁<br />\n巴打又係legal?<br />\n<br />\n(廁所透氣中)"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:39:01.000Z","msg":"同路人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公司有個同事次次都忍尿忍到最後一刻先去廁所<br />\n每次都聽到佢d痾尿聲勁大力，我遲過佢入去痾，我痾完洗埋手走佢都未痾完，成日都覺得佢咁樣好慘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:44:20.000Z","msg":"個自我大做咩者，個膀胱大咪得"},{"pid":"5698b19962f37a248213998e1d5a3d368c26a4e1","tid":939542,"uid":213877,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T11:48:08.000Z","msg":"你出世果刻已經定撚左<br />\n<br />\n你老豆老母有錢有家底<br />\n<br />\n你首刷就係稀有"},{"pid":"e9de57c5eecdc8952193ec3ced5b696156631466","tid":939542,"uid":213877,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2f65f3bfbab6bcbf863f0f501ea2cf4cb48d038c","tid":939542,"uid":155197,"like":240,"dislike":27,"score":213,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:27:52.000Z","msg":"好心你勤力D,唔好咁懶啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T11:48:55.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩，勤力到比你月搵10萬<br />\n<br />\n你咪又係打一世工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a208a92e8a8be393b2241a41c0f3b36bbfba957","tid":939542,"uid":37133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1e9781fc81b9f6f594d42be77d0c97cd7e04674","tid":939542,"uid":206224,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"quote":{"pid":"97267a24c6101d3fe7852fe12ef3d4712eb44f49","tid":939542,"uid":37133,"like":78,"dislike":3,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:32:58.000Z","msg":"屌好似講緊自己個人生咁<br />\n巴打又係legal?<br />\n<br />\n(廁所透氣中)"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:39:01.000Z","msg":"同路人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公司有個同事次次都忍尿忍到最後一刻先去廁所<br />\n每次都聽到佢d痾尿聲勁大力，我遲過佢入去痾，我痾完洗埋手走佢都未痾完，成日都覺得佢咁樣好慘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T12:30:46.000Z","msg":"AS十幾萬ok啦， 好過好多人。 係灰啲同辛苦啲姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b724ba41490272dfdd313aaa4428b01a1a267a","tid":939542,"uid":83251,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T12:32:37.000Z","msg":"香港特騙行政區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2dba1f14c6848be29b5df244e21f388b17db6a","tid":939542,"uid":119330,"like":195,"dislike":2,"score":193,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T12:44:44.000Z","msg":"我就咁睇<br />\n勤勤力力 規規矩矩 按步就班<br />\n呢條真係一條路<br />\n好多前行已經行通左<br />\n問題係 條路真係太平 目標太明確<br />\n結果就係好多人都會行呢條路<br />\n亦因為咁 供求失衡情況下<br />\n就有無良老細諗縮數<br />\n反正你唔做 大把人做<br />\n<br />\n相反 人地做拉麵<br />\n有幾多人願意放棄白領工作<br />\n走入廚房做野<br />\n就算係入左廚房做野 其實都係睇錢份上<br />\n有幾多人真係努力去做<br />\n就算俾你過到日本去學整麵<br />\n你估付出既 真係少咩<br />\n<br />\n所以俗語有云<br />\n&quot;欲無後悔須修己 各有前因莫羨人&quot;"},{"pid":"915c8750579741e31352e93fd761b641f356b23a","tid":939542,"uid":138420,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T12:46:40.000Z","msg":"日本輕鬆d ? 真心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114d2fba09ab8840d3bd9427d888fc6937e0fe5e","tid":939542,"uid":49004,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:11:36.000Z","msg":"你睇人好 人睇你好"},{"pid":"7078ee0664bb2488811bb79f0d7e0bf959311a53","tid":939542,"uid":225733,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:14:16.000Z","msg":"高質"},{"pid":"69ac4811b7bf685f873795f41a7bd8f8db386b71","tid":939542,"uid":49004,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:15:04.000Z","msg":"係咪謊言根本唔重要<br />\n重點無論真假 你都係要硬食<br />\n一係繼續努力 一係轉工<br />\n人生係靠你自己創造"},{"pid":"f108bbf933b03cc955c5671af8d4052bcd7f7c68","tid":939542,"uid":138316,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:15:32.000Z","msg":"咁似steal job d 飛機文"},{"pid":"378871c6398e5fcabc63ef5e92ef189354c02fc3","tid":939542,"uid":72173,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:31:36.000Z","msg":"小學老師話升到好中學有好前途<br />\n中學老師話升到大學有好工做<br />\n出到黎邊個最假最識見工最靚女果個老闆咪請囉"},{"pid":"c79dfeec55638590f846011e5f6e74d1e4ae5b6f","tid":939542,"uid":54387,"like"