rl=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdNVZ0ZPfE8s&d=jWio4OM9S%2BpzTTpU6lxKII9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=c4d32f35\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dNVZ0ZPfE8s</a>"},{"pid":"3d0ef0c64d4446a0fd5bc1d77b397af7c10c7da4","tid":939542,"uid":141782,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:35:06.000Z","msg":"Inhouse 真係好撚爽皮<br />\n複雜d 都掟出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d658c6e44fa3fb7cf9b5412f76d1734c1c712fab","tid":939542,"uid":84367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:37:37.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"3ddfb00df546b364c60440c95a876de0bd921cf6","tid":939542,"uid":164980,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:37:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0e21b9ebb678c872d63908eb020990a5d37099b","tid":939542,"uid":4308,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:43:29.000Z","msg":"細細個你孝順父母<br />\n大個左先知係養兒防老"},{"pid":"73d8c85bdd2ae090a917c00b2328f639e9e8e9b5","tid":939542,"uid":88374,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:48:19.000Z","msg":"香港係太多人先搞到咁姐<br />\n踢走一半人就會慢慢正常返架啦<br />\n不過要賠上經濟"},{"pid":"adbc3702be25a856a7cd4362d9ce20e65613d15b","tid":939542,"uid":178800,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:50:52.000Z","msg":"唔單止咁,<br />\n明明現今新世代講公平,正常放工時間唔OT係基本要求<br />\n都會比人話你唔上進,唔捱得<br />\n根本係班老屎忽上哂岸啦,唔抵得新一代唔跟佢地果套捱世界模式<br />\n根本成個社會已經病態<br />\n<br />\n不過用例子黎比較都唔洗用日本,稍為了解時事都知日本辦公室奴隸文化仲衰過香港,就算無留意時事,連新桓BB套日劇都無睇就真係盲撐日本了<br />\n應該拎歐美做例子,成個故仔有說服力好多<br />\n5/10 分 (用日本做例子扣5分,如講JOHNNY仔去左歐美或澳洲學廚,咁就10/10了)"},{"pid":"c6de7f1957b83a1ed06a09db36e231ff694590c9","tid":939542,"uid":178800,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a82d10d4882f42a3f49bda8e19bee117e1a396ff","tid":939542,"uid":206224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:21:25.000Z","msg":"由小學開始，老師就開始兇鳩你話記缺點會對未來有好大影響<br />\n讀緊中學果陣，師長話努力讀書考到入大學就可以日日玩<br />\n辛苦入到大學之後，讀書刷GPA之餘仲要搏命刷CV做實習，因為個個都話到時入到份高薪厚職就可以呼風喚雨<br />\n點知就算你畢業做到專業人士，你都只不過係一個要攬曬所有屎黎做嘅低層。你個老闆會同你講：拿，你日日爆肝OT係有回報嘅，捱兩三年之後升職，到時咩福利都有你嘆<br />\n勞勞役役三年後，你發覺老闆根本無諗過升你職，人工加得雞碎咁多之餘，其他福利反而cut q埋。好唔忿氣嘅你聽到同事話，阿Tom係間公司做5年之後成功跳槽入到去in-house，可以日日點鳩外面嘅人做野，幾撚爽皮<br />\n你憑住呢個信念捱到有5年經驗，如願以償跳槽入到去in-house。點知你發覺間公司一樣要OT到凌晨，人工升幅都係追唔到物價，因為香港老闆根本大部分都係刻薄吸血鬼黎。As long as你仲係香港呢個圈子到，你就永遠係要被壓逼果個。<br />\n<br />\n有晚，你如常OT到凌晨先返到屋企，沖完涼之後臨訓打開facebook望下<br />\n你見到中學果個成日比老師鬧死蠢，入唔到大學嘅Johnny仔post左張好靚嘅日本風景相。<br />\nJohnny仔中學畢業就去日本一間拉麵店做學徒，日日準時開工收工，個日本老闆都好均真地將一切所識用心教Johnny仔。幾年之後，Johnny仔跟師傅返去日本總店做野，靠工作簽證拎埋永住權。雖然人工唔高，但而家有一棟自己嘅獨立屋，兩架車，同老婆恩恩愛愛咁生活落去，weekend都可以揸車去趟road trip。<br />\n你不禁反問自己，明明你聽曬師長所講，付出比其他人更多嘅努力，拎住份叫做OK嘅人工。點解你嘅生活質素依然每況越下，甚至要比Johnny仔漸漸拋離？<br />\n呢一晚你突然領悟到，香港根本係個超巨型奴隸社會。上層嘅人呃鳩中層人，中層人再呃鳩下層人，誘導班奴隸繼續係香港賣命，為班上層嘅人做狗。<br />\n殺人放火金腰帶，修橋補路無屍骸。<br />\n係香港做野嘅人生，根本只係一層又一層嘅謊言。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:51:49.000Z","msg":"唔單止咁,<br />\n明明現今新世代講公平,正常放工時間唔OT係基本要求<br />\n都會比人話你唔上進,唔捱得<br />\n根本係班老屎忽上哂岸啦,唔抵得新一代唔跟佢地果套捱世界模式<br />\n根本成個社會已經病態<br />\n<br />\n不過用例子黎比較都唔洗用日本,稍為了解時事都知日本辦公室奴隸文化仲衰過香港,就算無留意時事,連新桓BB套日劇都無睇就真係盲撐日本了<br />\n應該拎歐美做例子,成個故仔有說服力好多<br />\n5/10 分 (用日本做例子扣5分,如講JOHNNY仔去左歐美或澳洲學廚,咁就10/10了)"},{"pid":"213c9331606285511a5246fb10778c0ad0109102","tid":939542,"uid":110375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a52bc5b74888cd6cc86e6197bc7a177d565a4d4","tid":939542,"uid":20809,"like":86,"dislike":3,"score":83,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:40:05.000Z","msg":"每年放榜拎狀元既學生都有10個8個，就係要報導d來自公屋、單親、父母有病...等等既學生<br />\n<br />\n傳媒又會報導下d窮撚創業成功<br />\n<br />\n又有d標題曾經公屋仔，依家做醫生律師之類<br />\n<br />\n呃鳩d窮人以為努力就會成功，個社會會進步，經濟有增長，都係靠d窮撚以為有希望黎推動。<br />\n100個人都咁努力，只有1個人會成功，社會就賺左99個渴望成功既人既生產力。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:53:13.000Z","msg":"因為你會 希望自己係嗰一個"},{"pid":"f437a98720dca2e55cc6f9eb79f53535cd70ca37","tid":939542,"uid":154793,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:54:46.000Z","msg":"Johnny仔敢行出自己comfort zone<br />\n有勇氣去行一條唔知結果嘅路，抵佢成功嘅<br />\n你順從權威 諗住跟前人成功嘅做法就衰極有限<br />\n都冇得怨，條路自己揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b60b8b47a86d94f7b41117ef6f1c56e07a2cb5","tid":939542,"uid":75139,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:55:05.000Z","msg":"樓主個johnny咪又係一個謊言<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好地地會收外人做學徒咩"},{"pid":"668e3b9a488ee6941ad5041ad04667749563f28c","tid":939542,"uid":225828,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:11:23.000Z","msg":"聽話仔的一生(毒男的一生)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc7c28a3d983b3cc59d35ef7bbe66e205ea35c9","tid":939542,"uid":225828,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a82d10d4882f42a3f49bda8e19bee117e1a396ff","tid":939542,"uid":206224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:21:25.000Z","msg":"由小學開始，老師就開始兇鳩你話記缺點會對未來有好大影響<br />\n讀緊中學果陣，師長話努力讀書考到入大學就可以日日玩<br />\n辛苦入到大學之後，讀書刷GPA之餘仲要搏命刷CV做實習，因為個個都話到時入到份高薪厚職就可以呼風喚雨<br />\n點知就算你畢業做到專業人士，你都只不過係一個要攬曬所有屎黎做嘅低層。你個老闆會同你講：拿，你日日爆肝OT係有回報嘅，捱兩三年之後升職，到時咩福利都有你嘆<br />\n勞勞役役三年後，你發覺老闆根本無諗過升你職，人工加得雞碎咁多之餘，其他福利反而cut q埋。好唔忿氣嘅你聽到同事話，阿Tom係間公司做5年之後成功跳槽入到去in-house，可以日日點鳩外面嘅人做野，幾撚爽皮<br />\n你憑住呢個信念捱到有5年經驗，如願以償跳槽入到去in-house。點知你發覺間公司一樣要OT到凌晨，人工升幅都係追唔到物價，因為香港老闆根本大部分都係刻薄吸血鬼黎。As long as你仲係香港呢個圈子到，你就永遠係要被壓逼果個。<br />\n<br />\n有晚，你如常OT到凌晨先返到屋企，沖完涼之後臨訓打開facebook望下<br />\n你見到中學果個成日比老師鬧死蠢，入唔到大學嘅Johnny仔post左張好靚嘅日本風景相。<br />\nJohnny仔中學畢業就去日本一間拉麵店做學徒，日日準時開工收工，個日本老闆都好均真地將一切所識用心教Johnny仔。幾年之後，Johnny仔跟師傅返去日本總店做野，靠工作簽證拎埋永住權。雖然人工唔高，但而家有一棟自己嘅獨立屋，兩架車，同老婆恩恩愛愛咁生活落去，weekend都可以揸車去趟road trip。<br />\n你不禁反問自己，明明你聽曬師長所講，付出比其他人更多嘅努力，拎住份叫做OK嘅人工。點解你嘅生活質素依然每況越下，甚至要比Johnny仔漸漸拋離？<br />\n呢一晚你突然領悟到，香港根本係個超巨型奴隸社會。上層嘅人呃鳩中層人，中層人再呃鳩下層人，誘導班奴隸繼續係香港賣命，為班上層嘅人做狗。<br />\n殺人放火金腰帶，修橋補路無屍骸。<br />\n係香港做野嘅人生，根本只係一層又一層嘅謊言。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:11:41.000Z","msg":"Welcome to Hong Kong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5401740a6b225c8ff063d6d40818c0b945d583ff","tid":939542,"uid":34222,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:13:53.000Z","msg":"循規蹈矩不嬲冇錯 只係唔會餓死 又唔會發達姐<br />\n成功既人都係要破格架啦 <br />\n 不過好多人寧願留係comfort zone 唔願冒險 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b426ee471709a3c3629950a94775ae7bd4f14919","tid":939542,"uid":356,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:16:42.000Z","msg":"講到出黎做野之後根本係你睇人好姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個都唔會po唔開心野上Facebook<br />\n你就當曬人日日都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呀Johnny仔比師傅屌 <br />\n日本老婆拎曬佢份糧你又唔知姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83aea12783965fc5a0d9a1942b961e674ebafc8","tid":939542,"uid":86509,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:20:28.000Z","msg":"睇下&ldquo;人類大歷史&rdquo;呢本書<br />\n你就明所有嘢只係故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d6619aeef1ec5db19c84f6e6a14ae4b57f6a41","tid":939542,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:22:05.000Z","msg":"呢篇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁似mk仔同毒撚嗰篇咁既"},{"pid":"7b7e13c81bea98c15c88250b466ec0b810175a66","tid":939542,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8ed48bada03579349c07c3334d169bc47aafd43","tid":939542,"uid":62337,"like":150,"dislike":19,"score":131,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:33:13.000Z","msg":"因為你無用腦獨立地思考同為自己打算 剩係識聽人點 <br />\n順便可以賴埋環境造成自己咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:25:33.000Z","msg":"咪係，係醒既就算身邊既人點反對點9up都好，自己做足資料搜集一樣可以好似Johnny 仔咁移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f95fd973452aeab51cff82e7cbf9c70835034b","tid":939542,"uid":137157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:27:45.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪做engine"},{"pid":"85958a55c92b8e397eea6856a42d5005b801d42f","tid":939542,"uid":147519,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:55:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TOT7mBO5-NM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTOT7mBO5-NM&d=jWio4OM9S%2BpzTTpU6lxKII9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=6753f9c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TOT7mBO5-NM</a>"},{"pid":"eaec23c71508c8525b6db9edd00141be3bbba560","tid":939542,"uid":118314,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T14:06:27.000Z","msg":"Johnny仔日日比師傅屌老母又同你講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老豆無錢人生就會痛苦，就係咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5d19c7ddf5354543eaf90f7375f3a5944ec0bc","tid":939542,"uid":182556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T14:14:32.000Z","msg":"唔講以為係自己開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c847c5e6fb877ca2b14cd5912bb912ab4a80e6fd","tid":939542,"uid":24335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T14:15:15.000Z","msg":"唔好講到咁白好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afeb2c16b0c46afe6e7a8ec5b4a1f874bdef9553","tid":939542,"uid":224107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T14:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人生就是帶著一種無奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f42c34546ce3cd53e2faa3eff533bd53647c3eb","tid":939542,"uid":30855,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T14:25:16.000Z","msg":"人既慾望係無窮無盡既<br />\n到你揾到一定既收入<br />\n你又會羨慕其他人擁有其他野<br />\n<br />\n所以人生係要知足常樂<br />\n呢句都係自欺欺人既謊言<br />\n但求安慰自己 好過一點<br />\n<br />\n思想愈簡單既人愈快樂<br />\n因為佢地唔會諗所謂人生既意義<br />\n有得食有得訓就夠<br />\n<br />\n活係呢個世代<br />\n改變唔到環境就唯有改變自己心態"},{"pid":"059fa41063ab2f0236aa91259676826006e30f00","tid":939542,"uid":206050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T14:38:19.000Z","msg":"好丑命生成<br />\n人生本無形<br />\n<br />\n你有野想傾訴可以留個tg"},{"pid":"30ad059e44b302a8758083b8f4c95963ccdf50ce","tid":939542,"uid":204424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T14:40:56.000Z","msg":"資本主義下的奴隸"},{"pid":"e372d9c26a06248b4d1af389718a1cebcdbd83f6","tid":939542,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T14:42:16.000Z","msg":"遲下有AI代工你想返工都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50957a0d463e18192df0e538d9502a79adeec964","tid":939542,"uid":27960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72cd72525788edff6e992e888adb5e85402721ab","tid":939542,"uid":48743,"like":61,"dislike":3,"score":58,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:53:59.000Z","msg":"其實你朋友開post曬命都係一種謊言，梗係post好野，唔通日日做到死死下又話你聽咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根本你無家底人生就辛苦好多，依個就係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔通細細個就同細路講你無架喇，你做到仆街一生人都搵唔到人地一日賺既錢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T14:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737bb01385c00ac6d90286093f3408b8055fcddc","tid":939542,"uid":18296,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T14:51:34.000Z","msg":"冇人夠你關心自己<br />\n所有人嘅&quot;指引&quot;, 唔多唔少都包含咗自己嘅私利<br />\n例如你讀得好，校長家長會讚老師，升職；叫你ot係為咗幫佢搵錢，唔係想教你嘢"},{"pid":"44ff49e951027341da2da3ea447fedb6ff922ce8","tid":939542,"uid":189638,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T14:53:51.000Z","msg":"聽人講即係跟人條路嚟行，如果係一個正常資本主義社會，你最多係中產，因為你缺乏去賭嘅勇氣。<br />\n<br />\n但做生意十個有九死，最後剩下嘅一個就係奴役你嘅老細。<br />\n<br />\n係極權社會，有關係就冇關係，只要你識人岸鳩都上到位，接單工程就幾千萬計，又可以權謀私，只限自己做嘅生意。但可惜係極權下你都係無背景。"},{"pid":"d9e4c1fbca85b4db0fa83044354a47e83688f466","tid":939542,"uid":160747,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T14:58:05.000Z","msg":"一命二運三風水，有d嘢唔係你可以控制到<br />\n<br />\n知足常樂～完"},{"pid":"0dc063f794af4b8b0659016fceb6245dcaaeb0b8","tid":939542,"uid":12013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T14:58:17.000Z","msg":"好彩有daddy 姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4472fabdbb1e9478c19296a4c0abc030557eed45","tid":939542,"uid":35129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:06:37.000Z","msg":"喊咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c79b8f373735214119f89fcadf5220ae6f32c4a","tid":939542,"uid":116910,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:07:46.000Z","msg":"關閪事咩<br />\n學歷比你最基本既野<br />\n成唔成功搵唔搵錢係睇個腦<br />\n<br />\n人叫你做乜你就做乜咪永遠做唔到第一個囉<br />\n咁咪注定幫人搵錢囉<br />\n有咩問題？"},{"pid":"be83e2de838d0115b105ffe8722137c893617758","tid":939542,"uid":58931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:07:55.000Z","msg":"發現新大陸?"},{"pid":"8b6b7df1e8d08b343f69763caf20b46f1ea717af","tid":939542,"uid":116910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:08:16.000Z","msg":"不過父幹決定一切<br />\n完"},{"pid":"7e97533b95f298f0d3184ff33de0b032a79bd02e","tid":939542,"uid":139830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:17:38.000Z","msg":"Johnny 仔咪又係謊言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a7d2eb5cec582e34dcead2a0ec7ce6d846b4d9","tid":939542,"uid":163972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T